collectionMetadata.name: Number of Members under Housing Schemes & Net Amount Withdrawn as at end of Quarter
collectionMetadata.description: Number of members under Public Housing and Private Properties Schemes, and amount withdrawn as at end of quarter.

datasetMetadata.name: Net amount withdrawn under housing schemes as at end of quarter
datasetMetadata.description:
Net amount withdrawn under Public Housing (HDB flats) and Private Housing Schemes as at end of quarter.
Figures are rounded to the nearest hundred thousand dollars.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of members under housing schemes as at end of quarter
datasetMetadata.description:
Refers to number of members who withdrew under Public Housing (HDB flats) & Private Housing Scheme and still own property as at end of quarter. 
Figures for Public Housing Scheme are revised from 2014 onwards, due to changes in criteria defining PHS participation.
Figures are rounded to the nearest thousand.
